    <item>
      <title>Internet of things access control model based on blockchain and edge computing</title>
      <link>https://Xu-shan-shan.github.io/publication/journal-article/2022/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Apr 2021 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://Xu-shan-shan.github.io/publication/journal-article/2022/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://jackaugust.github.io/files/Internet_of_things_access_control_model_based_on_blockchain_and_edge_computing.pdf&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Download paper here&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This paper is about IoT security. In the cloud-edge-end architecture, try to implement access control based on blockchain and give a SC-ABAC model and a simple prototype. SC-ABAC is Smart Contract for Attribute-Based Access Control, and the POW consensus algorithm has been improved in the prototype.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Congratulations!!!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;
Until November 17, 2023, this paper was selected as a China Knowledge Network Academic Essentials &lt;strong&gt;Highly Cited Paper&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;Highly Downloaded Paper&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
